::Orchestra/Composer::

        Orchestra smiled.

          "Well, thank you for the compliment, but I'm sure you'd find my
brother Symphony even nicer" he said, but then his smile turned into a small
frown, then into an expression of hope.

            "I know my brothers are out there!  And when I find them, we can
leave this plan-" Orchestra paused, and looked at Blacknightmare.  He
would've said "leave this planet", but then he changed his mind.  He was
already enjoying just being a newbie to the Predacons and meeting this
spectacular fem-bot.

         "Then we can leave our troubles behind," He redid his sentence.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
          Composer looked at Wheeljack.

           "Well, if we got eveeything, let's get to work!"  He said
hartily.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
=="Brother!  Join the Alliance!  It is the path to victory!"    -Composer,
convincing Orchestra to join him-

(This quote is NOT part of my roleplay, every now-and-then I will post
little quotes that have been made by my chars, this one is different because
none of them have said it :):))
